    A class that provides some useful functionality for test classes that check implementations of the FordFulkerson-interface. It creates two valid (flowGraph1 and flowGraph2) and one invalid (flowGraph3) flow graph that can be used as test data for the findPath and augmentPath-methods in implementations of the FordFulkerson-interface. Also a directed, an undirected and a mixed graph are created for the use as test data for the findMaxFlow-method.
